Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃 我最喜欢巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,完全就是一条小狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,奏先生喜欢巧克力么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就叫巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 叫巧克力也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 稍微帅气一些叫裘可拉吧
